AR Draw Trace-Sketch and Paint
Privacy Policy
Thank you for choosing AR Draw Trace-Sketch and Paint. This privacy policy describes how we collect, use, and share information when you use our mobile application, AR Draw Trace-Sketch and Paint, to protect your privacy and ensure the security of your personal information. We are dedicated to providing a safe and enjoyable experience for all users of our app.
Information Collection and Use
We may also collect information on how the app is accessed and used. This usage data may include information such as device type, operating system version, unique device identifiers, app usage patterns, and other diagnostic data. We use this information to improve the functionality of our app, personalize your experience, and provide customer support.
Cookies
Our app does not use cookies.
Service Providers
We may employ third-party companies and individuals to facilitate our app:
Google ads
in-app purchase
to provide the app on our behalf, to perform app-related services, or to assist us in analyzing how our app is used.
Security
We prioritize the security of your personal information and employ appropriate measures to protect it against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
Links to other sites
Our app may contain links to other websites or applications that are not operated by us. If you click on a third-party link, you will be directed to that third-party's site. We strongly advise you to review the privacy policy of every site you visit.
Children Policy
Our app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so that we can take the necessary action.
Changes Policy
We reserve the right to update or change our privacy policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised privacy policy on this page.
In-App Purchases
Our app may offer in-app purchases for additional features or an ad-free experience. Any purchases made within the app are subject to our terms of service and the policies of the platform from which you downloaded the app (e.g., Apple App Store, Google Play Store).
Advertisement
Our app may display advertisements served by Google Mobile Ads. Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on our app based on your prior visits to our app and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to our users based on their visits to our app and other sites on the Internet.
Permissions
Camera, Microphone Permissions, and Storage: We may request access to your device's camera, microphone, and storage to enable you to utilize certain app features, such as capturing images or recording audio for drawing purposes. This data is solely used within the app and is not transmitted to our servers or stored externally.
